from a in db->FLSpopodrazdeleniyu where AND(a->Podrazdelenie->Roditelskoepodrazdelenie == $Roditelskoepodrazdelenie, OR(GREATER(a->FLSRef->Srok, NOW()), EQUALS(FORMAT("{0:dd.MM.yyyy}", LIST(a->FLSRef->Srok)), "01.01.0001") )) select a->FLSRef->id
from a in db->FLS where OR(GREATER(a->Srok, NOW()), EQUALS(FORMAT("{0:dd.MM.yyyy}", LIST(a->Srok)), "01.01.0001") ) select a->id
